{"tid":2346201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街坊擋鑽挖機救鬼斧神工 「冇諗過香港有咁靚嘅地方」","createTime":"2020-12-30T05:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T06:00:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae127b31ebd5870cf10e788b82d93e79472fbbc","tid":2346201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/JTN3K3H3KJDEHH2RFBU3GDPL3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FJTN3K3H3KJDEHH2RFBU3GDPL3A%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=e85fc79b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FJTN3K3H3KJDEHH2RFBU3GDPL3A%2F&h=5c66eb72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/JTN3K3H3KJDEHH2RFBU3GDPL3A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n街坊擋鑽挖機救鬼斧神工<br />\n「冇諗過香港有咁靚嘅地方」<br />\n<br />\n【拯救古蹟】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：水務署黑照片誤導區會<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】座落石硤尾平民區的小山，因逾百年歷史配水庫重見天日而聲名大噪。多年來在主教山晨操晚練的街坊赫然發現鄰家原來暗藏珍貴古蹟，不惜擅闖地盤意圖制止清拆工程。被禾稈埋藏多年的珍珠亦引來區外人前來朝聖，有攝影師大嘆羅馬式蓄水池神奇，期望政府好好保育。<br />\n<br />\n主教山頂本來是個晨運客熱點，未動工前放滿鐵製韆鞦和各式健身架，還有乒乓波枱和竹枝搭建的小涼亭。本周日，街坊芳姐趁假期登山，發現山頂挖出大洞，內裏暗藏龐然建築，「當時見到，嘩！啲柱好靚喎！仲有幾條，之後就落去睇同影相，仲發畀朋友叫佢哋過嚟，係最後打卡時間，見證歷史，聽日不再㗎喇。我一路感受好心痛、好不捨，真係流眼淚。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民建聯爭取發展稱居民訴求<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e2b6jRjlNkzTTd1SOJsresKOsbk=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5OPP2CYQ6RESVJ5RU25P22HLO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe2b6jRjlNkzTTd1SOJsresKOsbk%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5OPP2CYQ6RESVJ5RU25P22HLO4.jpg&h=1e51ed37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■主教山蓄水池因工程重見天日，有市民慕名前往，一睹這個逾百年歷史的古蹟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份拱門石柱已損壞<br />\n<br />\n芳姐其後聯絡一眾街坊翌日晨早上山，趕在工人動工前抗議，「有街坊鬧我黐線嘅，政府要拆嘅嘢就要拆㗎啦，咁多事。我答唔到佢，我就係心痛。」但工人無視抗議，繼續發動鑽挖機，她於是爬入圍封範圍，走近電鑽意圖關掉機器，成功迫使工人停工。<br />\n<br />\n至昨晨，主。。。。。。。。。。配水庫部份紅磚砌成的拱門和石柱已遭破壞，碎片遺留在內。蓄水池內仍留有水位刻度和大水管，雖然看似已生銹，但目測結構完整。<br />\n<br />\n已在主教山晨運十多年的街坊陳女。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kotnEnmgE9dTNcNrgETUSP3PO9I=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYGLWQEYPRE7TK34ZNKIMZS3GM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkotnEnmgE9dTNcNrgETUSP3PO9I%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYGLWQEYPRE7TK34ZNKIMZS3GM.jpg&h=46043163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蓄水池內仍留有大水管，雖略現銹迹仍結構完整。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x_VcIFlSZk88-DnVdHrZ1UPddSM=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V3XEW3LRDBGXJDMUMI6VARPETM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx_VcIFlSZk88-DnVdHrZ1UPddSM%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV3XEW3LRDBGXJDMUMI6VARPETM.jpg&h=de1fc70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一名街坊日前走近鑽挖機，意圖迫使工人停工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公眾登山遭票控犯聚<br />\n<br />\n旅遊攝影師李先生特意到來，從鐵絲網外觀察古蹟，「香港好少有咁舊嘅遺蹟，同埋政府想拆咗佢，靠民間力量先停工」。他曾遊覽的土耳其伊斯坦堡也有類似蓄水池，「冇諗過香港都有咁嘅地方，香港真係好有歷史，所以先有咁神奇嘅地方。應該保育佢，唔係問都冇問就填咗佢，當無事發生」。<br />\n<br />\n周日凌晨發文公開主教山配水庫的fb專頁「香港探故」負責人、保育建築。。。。。。。。。。設計更十分罕見。Nicky認為，水務署在動工前應先研究配水庫歷史，「唔係咁草率就提交畀區議會」，古蹟辦更無事前實地碪察，「開工之前應該做好study」。<br />\n<br />\n周一起大量公眾人士前來欲一睹古羅馬建築，當局在工地拉上鐵閘禁止外人進入，並有保安員通宵留守，周一晚入夜後仍有人到來，部份人被警方票控違反限聚令。警方表示，前晚11時20分接報，懷疑有人於主教山配水庫聚集。警員到場調查後，發現八名男子（20歲至51歲）涉嫌違反限聚令，予以票控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vV19bwPje1lb4a5KpU4jKom--Tc=/457x504/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WTLIMLO5QBEKPLEVZHP5ZZEH64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvV19bwPje1lb4a5KpU4jKom--Tc%3D%2F457x504%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWTLIMLO5QBEKPLEVZHP5ZZEH64.jpg&h=1e4d9210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663a1fcdab9ed3585a82e7e8321493ec9b472650","tid":2346201,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"發你老母"},{"pid":"dd089d7cb1bc72a9c03e0d0a33a23d3f562daaba","tid":2346201,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohW5nVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohW5nVn.jpg&h=c1de6c5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1131082b14052c3b8c5f77184900295cc1dc82ba","tid":2346201,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"唔覺靚<br />\n比我入到去<br />\n會有幽閉恐懼症"},{"pid":"ed01904fd72d68540de192a7d95bedeac1d89a6c","tid":2346201,"uid":61511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1131082b14052c3b8c5f77184900295cc1dc82ba","tid":2346201,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"唔覺靚<br />\n比我入到去<br />\n會有幽閉恐懼症"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"多謝你既個人意見<br />\n<br />\n唔靚都可以有歷史價值既"},{"pid":"1abd505fb3f2aae3fcd415dbf3af0791f6191fba","tid":2346201,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}